{"tid":149154,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[純球例討論] 根本球十二碼就唔關隻手事","createTime":"2017-03-09T05:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T11:07:13.000Z","uid":72652,"like":23,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94ccf17cc47d039d012edb8f1b54485a55cc14b6","tid":149154,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/X0uGmSkj5QH8k/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FX0uGmSkj5QH8k%2Fgiphy.gif&h=fb2947e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明主要係隻腳click到so9<br />\n<br />\n但當然蘇狗係全心搏十二碼<br />\n放軟哂個人<br />\n而且從球證角度<br />\nSo9食哂成個身位<br />\n下一秒就可以奪取控球權攻門<br />\n<br />\n係個後衛衰on9<br />\n禁區內一下呢d細動作影響一個直接的威脅攻勢<br />\n而又唔係五五波大家都有可能有控球權<br />\n<br />\n你可以屌so9誇大動作<br />\n以佢的身體質素絕對可以唔跌<br />\n亦可以話球證嚴<br />\n但球證絕對冇吹錯<br />\n<br />\n成班連登仔反疤條氣唔順搵野黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即管睇下聽日外國媒體/知名球星點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好心啦<br />\n十幾廿歲人<br />\n好下放低執著<br />\n做人會開心好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.s 盲反/盲撐的人可以上一頁"},{"pid":"3bfed9c89aee5b68225305044d147d34f5059020","tid":149154,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:47:17.000Z","msg":"係呀，就算接觸幾輕微，馬昆奴斯係禁區的確從後阻止左蘇9一個單刀起腳機會<br />\n蘇9係擺明搏十二碼，但呢球根本絕對可以吹<br />\n<br />\n華拉堤賽後都話呢場輸自己，唔關球證事"},{"pid":"51edb30cc59574c54d8cd3c7edc8185d77291a06","tid":149154,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"另一個角度明顯頂左埋去啦"},{"pid":"0986c7bad6b695273ea2b2bd843f706ad50a44c0","tid":149154,"uid":28734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"不過蘇狗演技真心唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落緊地就摸住個頭<br />\n到地就鍊住條頸<br />\n唔睇前面仲以為開掙批左落去"},{"pid":"5ce76421a41f656ff3e5951b44f3d16630cc04b9